tan and laundry by dado


27 May 2018 21:28






In waste management by dado, dado mentions that he runs a laundry and tan service. I have decided to write that, the joke being that there is nothing anomalous about dado's laundry. He's a brilliant entrepreneur and true capitalist who dabbles in washing machines, anomalous drugs and tanning beds. (But not anomalaundry)

NOTE:  The second sentence the Receptionist says is a question that ends in a period. This is an intentional stylistic choice to convey the apathy of the Receptionist, not an error.

